*) Check if this is the lastest version of rhms before you run any script:
   http://code.google.com/p/rhms/downloads/list

*) Wiki page (include step-by-step tutorial):
   http://code.google.com/p/rhms/wiki/RHEL_Mail_Server_Solution

*) Please do read the usage page before you run any script in rhms:
   http://code.google.com/p/rhms/wiki/rhms_Usage

*) Issue tracker & bug report:
   http://code.google.com/p/rhms/issues/list

*) Community (Chinese only):
   http://www.osspinc.com/bbs/

*) Quick Installation Guide:

   # cd /path/to/rhms-x.y.z/
   # cd pkgs/
   # sh get_all.sh
   # cd ../
   # sh rhms.sh
